<th>Used virtual space
</th>
<th>Total virtual space
</th>
<th colspan="2">Ratio
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td rowspan="2">Protected mode (non-PAE)
</td>
<td>4 KiB
</td>
<td style="text-align: right;">4 MiB
